     F** UEXR09A *****************************************************
     F*  PROGRAM: GET HONDA DELIVERY CODE FROM PLANT/SHIPTO CODE     *
     F*  WRITTEN: JW (SRA) 2024.11.01                                *
     F*--------------------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UEXR09A'
     F*                    PARM           $PLNT   3
     F*                    PARM           $SHCD  10
     F*                    PARM           $TOKU   4
     F*                    PARM           $NONY   4
     F*  IN  $PLNT :  3A PLANT CODE
     F*  "   $SHCD : 10A SHIP TO CODE
     F*  OUT $TOKU :  4A DELIVERY CODE (ERROR: 0000)
     F*  "   $NONY :  4A DELIVERY CODE (ERROR: 0000)
     F******************************************************
     FAB#PPHN IF  E           K        DISK
