     C                     PARM           $SHCD  10        "
     C                     PARM           $TOKU   4        OUT
     C                     PARM           $NONY   4        "
      *
 |   C           K#SHC     KLIST
 |   C                     KFLD           K@PLNT  3
 |   C                     KFLD           K@SHCD 10
      *
     C                     MOVE '0000'    $TOKU
     C                     MOVE '0000'    $NONY
      *
     C                     ENDSR
